ZH: 我要向所有关心和帮助我的人表示致谢。
EN: I want to express my thanks to everyone who has cared for and helped me.

ZH: 他的慷慨解囊值得致谢。
EN: His generosity is worthy of thanks.

ZH: 在这艰难的时刻，我们真的需要向他们致谢。
EN: At this difficult moment, we really need to thank them.

ZH: 我想代表全家向您表示我们的致谢。
EN: I want to express our thanks on behalf of the whole family.

ZH: 必须致谢你的耐心和合作。
EN: I must thank you for your patience and cooperation.

ZH: 我要致谢那些无私奉献的医护人员。
EN: I want to thank the selfless medical staff.

ZH: 在即将结束的一年里，请允许我向您致谢。
EN: As the year draws to a close, allow me to express my thanks to you.

ZH: 请接受我最诚挚的致谢。
EN: Please accept my sincerest thanks.

ZH: 我们深表致谢，没有您的帮助我们无法取得成功。
EN: We deeply thank you, without your help, we would not have been successful.

ZH: 我们致谢每一个为此项目贡献心力的人。
EN: We thank everyone who has contributed to this project.

ZH: 我们感到无法用语言表达对您的致谢之情。
EN: We are unable to express in words our gratitude to you.

ZH: 十分感谢你为我们提供的帮助，致谢无以为报。
EN: Thank you very much for your help, there is no way to repay your kindness.

ZH: 请允许我们向您致谢，感谢您一直以来对我们的支持。
EN: Allow us to thank you for your continuous support.

ZH: 对于您的善举，我深表致谢。
EN: I deeply thank you for your kindness.

ZH: 请接受我最衷心的致谢与祝福。
EN: Please accept my most heartfelt thanks and blessings.

ZH: 我们致谢那些一直支持我们的人。
EN: We thank those who have always supported us.

ZH: 让我们一同致谢这些无私奉献的志愿者们。
EN: Let us thank these selfless volunteers together.

ZH: 我在这里代表全体员工向您致谢。
EN: I am here on behalf of all the employees to express our thanks to you.

ZH: 衷心向您致谢，感激您毫不犹豫地伸出援助之手。
EN: Sincerely thank you for extending a helping hand without hesitation.
